{
  "texts": [
    "FA-LSTM applies an attention mechanism to assign weights for distinct features in the input vector.",
    "In this study, for soil moisture prediction, the feature attention mechanism in FA-LSTM processes the input vector I {x t-3,.",
    ".x t }, where x t = {f 1 t, f 2 t,.",
    ".f n t } and generates the weighted output x t-3.",
    "Through the attention mechanism, the output x t remains the same dimension size as the input x t."
  ]
}